        "action": "Exempt essential works from any income tax increase",
        "additional_details": "The financial costs of the Covid-19 outbreak will create a significant burden for tax payers, and essential worker should not be penalised for this.",
        "background": "The Government should support essential workers by exempting them from any income tax increases that are required as a result of Covid-19. Essential works have been working during this period and putting themselves at risk whilst many others have been able to work from home or be furloughed.",
